mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，增强激情跨越的&ldquo;士气&rdquo;。要围绕&ldquo;用心做事、团结共事、依法办事&rdquo;的政府工作准则，强化依法行政的&ldquo;公心&rdquo;、团结干事的&ldquo;真心&rdquo;、清正廉洁的&ldquo;良心&rdquo;，不断加强政府自身建设，努力提高政府公信力，树立良好的政府形象。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂要求，下一阶段，各镇、政府各部门要全力推进项目建设、不遗余力招商引资、认真组织春耕备耕、纵深推进&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动、深入开展治庸问责，以更高的标准抓好工作落实，以更快的节奏推进项目建设，以强烈的事业心和责任感、昂扬向上的精神状态、务实进取的工作作风，乘势而上，克难奋进，为加快建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城而努力奋斗。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会上，余珂与每位副县长及各镇镇长签订了相关工作责任书。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委常委、常务副县长熊武华主持会议，并就贯彻落实会议精神，认真办理县党代会、县&ldquo;两会&rdquo;代表和委员提出的提案、提议、议案、建议等工作做了要求。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">副县长饶自斌传达了市政府全会精神。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">副县长李德炳通报了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年政府工作报告&ldquo;十件实事&rdquo;进展情况。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
